&lt;p&gt;West Hertfordshire Hospitals NHS Trust&lt;br /&gt; Associated University (UCL) NHS Provider Trust&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Locum Consultant Anaesthetist &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Applications are invited for a Locum Consultant Anaesthetist at Watford General and St Albans City Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; The successful applicant will join a team of 35 Consultants, 15 Specialist Grade, and 35 Trainee anaesthetists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must be fully registered with the GMC, and have a CCT in Anaesthesia or be within 6 months of award of CCT at the time of interview.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested anaesthetists may contact Dr Aruna Navapurkar, Clinical Director on 01923 217604&lt;/p&gt;
